I am fully aware that this is questionable behaviour for a 23 year old woman to be playing porridge party with a collection of Halloween toys but I just L🎃VE this time of the year and all the spooks that come with it!!! For reals it just speaks to me on a different level haha I know loads of you are the same 👻🕸🍂 

Today’s little party bowl contained:
30g gluten free porridge oats
1 tbsp @peanut_hottie_official PB powder
1 tbsp coco powder
Water
Banana ghosts 👻
Plum pumpkins 🎃
@lotusbiscoffus graves ⚰️
1 tbsp @wholeearthfoods smooth PB
Blackberries, blueberries & red currants
Dried currants, desiccated coconut & seed mix
And a whole lot of spook 🧟‍♀️ 

Also please don’t ask me how long it took me to dress this bowl because I’m uncomfortable with the sheer amount of time I spent playing about and it DEFINITELY wasn’t stone cold by the time I got round to munching on it 👀👀 I swear.... 🥺🤣 

Anyway porridge peeps have a beautiful Wednesday! We all feeling festive yet?? All my love! 🧡

Homemade little creation (bit off topic) : A STRAWBERRY PIE 🍓🍰 ! 😻

We publish a lot of sometime complex recipe, today we've made something simple and seasonal. Hope you'll like it, recipe bellow ---- 🥧 For the shortcrust pastry: 250 g of flour, 125 g of caster sugar, 1 egg, 100 g of butter, 1 lemon zest, 1 pinch of salt  In a bowl, mix the egg with powdered sugar and a pinch of salt.  Put the flour on the worktop, make a well in the center, pour the contents of the bowl and the lemon zest, then the melted butter (especially not liquid butter!). Mix everything until you get a homogeneous paste. Roll it out.  Bake in a hot oven for 12 to 15 minutes. Possibility to put aluminum foil on it, to be sure it doesn't burn. 🍰 Mix the mascarpone with 80g of sugar and 1 and a half sachets of vanilla sugar, add the strawberries cut in half, set aside in the fridge and serve fresh.  #foodphotography #piercings #strawberry #foodie #strawberrycheesecake #strawberrys #instafoods #pie #prilaga #strawberryblonde #foodgasm #instafood #pier #instafoodapp #piercing #foodporn #food #foodstagram #strawberryshortcake #instafoodies #instafoodie #pies #pierced #strawberrycake

Tom Nook, Timmy & Tommy butter cookies!!💰 I must have been living under a rock to not know about Animal Crossing until recently (it's been around since 2001!!😲). Now I see it everywhere and really want to play it, except Ninetento Switch is apparently sold out globally (?) thanks to social distancing.  Plus, not sure if I need yet another mobile device…I'm already trying hard to cut down time spent on my smartphone.  So, I've just been watching other people play on YouTube instead, which is oddly relaxing.😅 Did you know that Tom Nook is so rich that he was featured on the front page of the Financial Times?🤣

I particularly enjoy this style of cookie making because it's almost entirely cookie dough.  In my case, the only non-cookie components are the red ties on the bell bags and the painted detailings.
